{"tid":2207713,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"平遙古城再遭共產  縣政府財困 逼遷224戶","createTime":"2020-09-18T10:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T11:17:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9fd973d7cbd06ac8777a8c83ec4bcf9a9148bc4c","tid":2207713,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:44:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200918/D3RNCH4SPVFLFNLMYTU3TTO5MA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200918%2FD3RNCH4SPVFLFNLMYTU3TTO5MA%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=3ea06d20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200918%2FD3RNCH4SPVFLFNLMYTU3TTO5MA%2F&h=8a53a27c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200918/D3RNCH4SPVFLFNLMYTU3TTO5MA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n平遙古城再遭共產 <br />\n縣政府財困 逼遷224戶<br />\n<br />\n名列世界文化遺產的山西平遙古城，城內的私有祖屋1958年被收歸國有，原屋主後人改革開放後歷經艱辛終討回房產。但當地政府卻在籌劃平遙古城上市之際，先後向224戶發出通知，推翻原來返還房產的決定，要求他們限期內搬走。有分析認為事件重演五十年代的「共產風」，估計隨着不少地方政府財困，還會發生同類事件。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大躍進強收私房分租貧民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/v8x1irE1CDiR2FewbZVXRUMnd3g=/683x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OEGXQKWJORCW3LJC4BIYC7UEYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fv8x1irE1CDiR2FewbZVXRUMnd3g%3D%2F683x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOEGXQKWJORCW3LJC4BIYC7UEYA.jpg&h=47c883b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有抗議的屋主被公安強行拖走。<br />\n<br />\n位於山西晉中市平遙縣的平遙古城，近期有多戶民房和客棧被公安查封上鎖，引起居民強烈不滿。事源今年6月以來，不少屋主先。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oRKYwsLcc1aMdlULvDmVnxDpZY0=/2362x1608/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O3UJ62MIOVCSNOIKLBE3HUE3WI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoRKYwsLcc1aMdlULvDmVnxDpZY0%3D%2F2362x1608%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO3UJ62MIOVCSNOIKLBE3HUE3WI.jpg&h=e16e6b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■山西平遙古城舉世馳名，名列聯合國世界文化遺產。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上世紀被徵收 屋主得而復失<br />\n<br />\n告知書稱，晉中市2018年對平遙縣經租房退還問題進行專項巡查後，認為在退還過程中，錯誤地為「地富資」（地主、富農和資本家）落實了私房政策，違反了國家制訂的「地富資」所有出租房產都要接受「社會主義改造」的政策。此次整改中涉及224戶，其中66戶是「地富資」，其餘158戶涉及2008年後通過貨幣置換方式取得物業產權的業主。<br />\n<br />\n位於南大街171號的平遙寶裕源客棧，房產持有人趙培金向本報稱，客棧曾於2018年翻新，雖然個別業主提出維權，但縣政府不。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5zjpNYd8gArCW11qCgx83g9xPTU=/843x750/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SLAM5FUQSFH25MNSQ7DR6KSAP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5zjpNYd8gArCW11qCgx83g9xPTU%3D%2F843x750%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSLAM5FUQSFH25MNSQ7DR6KSAP4.jpg&h=3282f869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n零協商空間 單位遭強行封鎖<br />\n<br />\n平遙古城客棧業主竹燕（化名）指，當局單方面定下收房期限，又不予任何上訴空間或協商途徑，強行鎖起單位及貼上封條。「經租房十年前還給我們的時候，是破爛不堪的爛房子，我們投資巨款修好了，所以覺得很冤，平遙旅遊業發展起來以後，門面房的價值也增值了，翻了有十倍的價格吧。平遙縣政府眼紅了，它就說當時我錯了，我又不給你了，要強行收回。」<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹表示，中共建政初期國家經濟一窮二白，當時的「共產風」將。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《中國經營報》/《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/t7x0jupa82oeLkI2nQCYXRDZk6w=/2439x588/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FVNXGFBASZGQVCCJXHUMCOZ3A4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft7x0jupa82oeLkI2nQCYXRDZk6w%3D%2F2439x588%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFVNXGFBASZGQVCCJXHUMCOZ3A4.jpg&h=03b8a4e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcd4fa47870bb2770949cb302ffd106eac9a3b5e","tid":2207713,"uid":350350,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:46:13.000Z","msg":"香港人：<br />\n移民留返間屋收租先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352f9de4366ebb43588d65f4e7b683c642ea17e8","tid":2207713,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:55:41.000Z","msg":"共產黨所到之處 寸草不生"},{"pid":"ba1eba19a80f9b019498c2c12ca9e3922ea03e9c","tid":2207713,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83c7aa6d4a7c6a73f2fc61d397cccc7492a6bb80","tid":2207713,"uid":2110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:58:36.000Z","msg":"邊個唔交返間屋出黎就係搞獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795528b9c74ae1588596dfa0ce3db9d411ff3da8","tid":2207713,"uid":278219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:59:47.000Z","msg":"拎 d囡囡出黎做好過啦"},{"pid":"c128a726677cbda980fbd77769570b968eb3dc5e","tid":2207713,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:00:15.000Z","msg":"繼續沉默<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d54c3d368a6c14091363a14823f378736228bf","tid":2207713,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"共產黨總有方法奪取人民財產"},{"pid":"fd56feb84f6c276385cc183841a531b8312cbc15","tid":2207713,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:05:14.000Z","msg":"香港住村屋果班傻鳩最危<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9906a2976f487654c720150c3ec95128f20a92","tid":2207713,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:09:51.000Z","msg":"中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68e14f3a2859c2078ff207c17bbb7b3fd2a528b","tid":2207713,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"good job <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c51c7ce16ab78d4f2a2550c121a8c9128a08149","tid":2207713,"uid":339272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:17:25.000Z","msg":"快d到香港"}]}